headline: Alba Wheels Up International, LLC Announces Key Executive Appointments to Drive Strategic Growth in Finance and Global Trade
summary: Alba Wheels Up International, LLC is proud to announce the addition of two seasoned executives to its leadership team: Robert D. Bosley as Chief Financial Officer (CFO) and Alexandra Kleinschmidt as EVP Sales, Marketing, and Account Management.

headline: BizClik Unveils the 250 Companies Driving Sustainability in 2025
summary: London, UK – 9 SEPTEMBER 2025 – BizClik, the global media and events company, and its Sustainability Magazine brand, have unveiled the driving 250 Companies in Sustainability, recognising the world’s leading organisations driving progress in environmental responsibility, social impact, and corporate governance. headline: MedX Health Appoints Global Skin Science Leader Dr. Paul Matts as Strategic Advisor
summary: MISSISSAUGA, Ontario, September 09, 2025--MedX Health Corp. (TSXV: MDX), "MedX" or the "Company"), a global leader in teledermatology and non-invasive skin analysis, today announced the appointment of Dr. Paul J. Matts, internationally recognized skin scientist, biochemist and educator, as Strategic Advisor to the Company.
